Morrison to Stay Open Later to Boost Sales, CEO Says, FT Reports

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-05-03T01:14:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-03/morrison-to-stay-open-later-to-boost-sales-ceo-says-ft-reports.html
WM Morrison Supermarkets Plc (MRW)  is
planning to keep most of its 440 stores open to 9 p.m. or 10
p.m. in a bid to boost sales and productivity, the Financial
Times reported, citing an interview with Chief Executive Officer
Dalton Philips.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 